Correspondents responding to Bruccoli's attempts to
         identify W.W. Windstaff include Malcolm Cowley (1974 Aug 9);
         Morrill Cody (1974 Aug 19); Arch Whitehouse (1974 Sep 4);
         W.A.B. Douglas (1974 Sep 5); J.F. McDonald (1974 Sep 16);
         George Tweney (1974 Sep 25); Philip M. Flammer (1974 Oct 1);
         John M. Davies (1974 Nov 20); and David Emmerson (1974 Dec
         3).
